Text.string: End of the road for you!
TRAUNT'S THE NAME. DON'T FORGET IT.
This is it for you, Vault Hunter!
Come on in, guys! Party's just getting started!
Heat it up, cool it down!
Fight fire with fire! Also ice!
(sing-songy) Some like it hot, some like it cold!
What's wrong? You're so... HOT AND COLD.
How about a bit of both?!
Traunt's about to get reaaal hot!
Traunt's got a biiig surprise for you!
Just, uh, gimme a second to heat up!
What's up now? An ice wall, that's what!
